  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Santa Lucia is a traditional, family-run hotel in the heart of Minori. The lovely beach is just a two-minute walk away and the town’s restaurants, cafés and shops are easily reached. The Sammarco family have run the hotel for more than 50 years, so you’re in good hands when it comes to recommendations and how to get the most out of your stay here.</p>
<p>You’ll find cosy guest rooms, complete with modern amenities, and a welcoming feeling throughout the hotel, from the vietri tiles and sofas in the small bar to the home-cooked local food in the restaurant.</p>]]></description>
